      <title>南非即将迎来后种族隔离时代最激烈的选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-29/south-africa-heads-into-closest-election-in-decades-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非周三举行选举，这场选举似乎将重塑南非的政治格局。三十年来，南非由纳尔逊·曼德拉领导的政党主导。Joumanna Bercetche 和 Jennifer Zabasajja 在《地平线：中东和非洲》节目中讨论了此次选举。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-29/south-africa-heads-into-closest-election-in-decades-video</guid>
